Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:07.15,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It was only a small pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:11.25,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Feelings that were supposed to have collided were blocked,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:13.02,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,unable to reach the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:17.79,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Wishes get tangled up, hearts and hopes melt together...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:21.12,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,We almost lose sight of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:25.87,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Now matter how sad the past, no matter how dark the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:29.03,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Still, we have to stand up against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:33.17,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Because I'm sure that everyone is fighting at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:39.15,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha A's{\i1} will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:50.68,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Prayers echoing in the vast skies turn to miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:13.64,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Teardrops melt and flow into the blue of the middle of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:19.82,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I met a warmth that engulfs all without hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:22.85,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Just like the pure white snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.92,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Words that are honest no matter how far you go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:32.80,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,It moves me as I wear wings of steel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:38.33,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Each time I am hurt,\NI can become kinder
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:46.77,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,My only wish is to protect that smile of yours to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:53.82,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Memories of sadness engraved across the ages
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:02:00.16,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,You are an angel of light, catching them straight on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:05.96,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,An eternal blaze that stopped in my heart that day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.43,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Releasing the deep darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:15.80,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,It opens the door of freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:22.73,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Towards the strong, boundless future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:43.09,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Though Fate's Linker Core is severely damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,her life is not in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Just like what happened to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:50.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} absorbed it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it was while the {\i1}Arthra{\i0} was running.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:56.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We were able to help her out much faster than in your case, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:58.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,A while after the two of you departed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:04.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,the security systems at headquarters all went down from a hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:08.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That was why I couldn't give commands or even contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:11.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, it's my responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Because you got the system back up quickly, Amy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,you were able to contact the {\i1}Arthra{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:23.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And we were able to grab clear footage of that masked man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:30.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Their equipment is of the same system as used by the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:35.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone out there that can crack into it from the outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:36.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:41.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Getting past all firewalls and alarms to take the system down so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's just unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm shifting the units around right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but I have to think of a stronger way of blocking them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:53.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that they have that good an engineer over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.94,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they have an organization to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:00.17,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What I also heard from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The conditions, and how they interact with each other, are still unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:03.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:06.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,By the time I got there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,the masked man was already nowhere in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:10.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But she...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:13.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Signum was holding on to Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:18.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She said she had no excuse, but she wanted to relay that she was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:22.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Allex, any problem with the {\i1}Arthra{\i0} cruising about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:23.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,No problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then, this is a bit earlier than scheduled,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but we will return to command HQ aboard the {\i1}Arthra{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:30.27,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,All hands, back to your regular positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha, you need to go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:36.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If it's about Fate, then it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'll take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:50.49,Nanoha A's Title1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur0.5\frx-30\pos(476,547)}The Heartbreaking Decision and the Courageous Choice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So, we can say that we were saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,At the least, it is certain that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:02.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,he wants the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} to be completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:07.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he wants to use the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} once it is completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That can't be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:11.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I mean, even if he took the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} after it's completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.75,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,only our master can use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:17.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,At the point of completion, the {\i1}Meister{\i0} will have absolute power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There is no way threats or brainwashing would have any effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:25.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, we have heavy security around the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:30.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so I don't think there's any chance a threat will come for Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Just to be on the safe side,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:35.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Shamal, stay by our {\i1}Meister{\i0}'s side as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:36.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hey, when we finish the{\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:42.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and Hayate becomes our master for real,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:45.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,it's going to make\NHayate happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What's this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:49.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Meister{\i0} of the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} will have grand powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:54.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We, the guardians, know that better than anyone else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:57.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:02.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I think somehow we're forgetting something really important...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:42.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.94,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate! Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The hospital... an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}Don't move her. Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate, are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Commodore Lindy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Arf?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:19.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Arf has been at your side all night as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.78,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're aboard the {\i1}Arthra{\i0} right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:28.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You were attacked from behind during your battle in the desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and had been unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your Linker Core got absorbed a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but they say you will be fine soon.\NNo need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:38.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I was defeated, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Not even Bureau searchers could confirm this ambush beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so there's nothing you could have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. Did you not like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,No... It's not that\NI didn't like it... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:54.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You seemed to be having a nightmare, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.11,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But thank goodness you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I contacted the school and told them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that you will be absent due to family matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:07.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so you should rest a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}You're getting hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:15.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll bring a light meal and a drink.\NWhat would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:21.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well... I'll leave it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:34.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:42.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, you seem to be all right. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:45.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes... thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's why I said I got a bit dizzy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:52.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and pulled the muscles in my chest and hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:55.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Geez, everyone is making such a big deal out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:58.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But you did hit your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Had it been something, it would have been a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:03.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, since you came out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:09.05,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I would like to do a few tests, so relax here for a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Now, Ms. Signum and Ms. Shamal...\NA word over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:14.94,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:22.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nothing's showing up in the tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:26.27,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but I don't think it's just a pulled muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:29.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes. She seemed to be in great pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:32.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the paralysis is starting to spread again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She didn't have symptoms like this in the past, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I don't think she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:41.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But Hayate always hides all of her pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:44.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There is no guarantee that she won't have another seizure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It would be best for her to be hospitalized for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,just to be on the safe side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:50.78,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:54.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hospitalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, apparently so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:05.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it's just for testing to be on the safe side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So you have nothing to worry about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:13.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, that in itself is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:17.11,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But if I'm here in the hospital, who's going to cook for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:21.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'll... we'll... manage somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:25.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's right... it will be all right... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll come visit every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:29.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Vita, you're such a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't have to be every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:38.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to do here, so you'd get bored, Vita.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:45.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then I'll relax and spend a vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.11,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that comes with three meals and an afternoon nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:53.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Suzuka might be texting me and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:56.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, I will contact her for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:01.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then we'll go home and bring you some clothes and a few books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Do you have any requests?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What should I choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:21.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Vita?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:19.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Let me report what\NI've figured out so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:21.27,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,First of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:23.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} is not its original name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,According to the old resources,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:28.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,its real name is {\i1}Buch der Nachthimmel{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It was a tome that traveled with the {\i1}Meister{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:36.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,originally created to gather great magical technology from each land
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,for use as research material.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:41.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The use of destructive powers probably began when
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:46.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,the main program was altered by one of the users over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So people who abuse Lost Logia
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:53.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,to recklessly attempt to gain immense power
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,existed in the past as well as the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:59.78,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Because of that alteration, the travel function
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:03.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and the automatic repair of corrupted data are running out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:06.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is that the reason behind the reincarnation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:07.75,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and the infinite replays?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:10.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If it's ancient magic, that much might be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The worst part of it all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:15.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,are the changes to its owner's nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If there is no gathering of power for a certain period of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,it starts to eat away at the owner's magical powers and potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And when it's complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,the owner's magical powers will be used without limits,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,for indiscriminate destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That is why all the owners until now have,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,right after the completion of the {\i1}Buch{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:37.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What about material on methods for stopping or sealing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:39.75,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm looking up right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but stopping it before it's complete will probably be very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:43.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:47.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Only one the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} recognizes as the true {\i1}Meister{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:50.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,has administrator rights to the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:53.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,In other words, there is no other way to stop or change the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Upon forced controls from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:01.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,an embedded system will absorb the {\i1}Meister{\i0} and respawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:05.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's right. That is why they say
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:09.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that sealing the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} for good is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:11.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It started out as a wholesome research book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:13.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You know, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:17.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I also feel sorry for the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.78,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,the {\i1}Buch der Nachthimmel{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've researched?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:22.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,At this point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm still looking up all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.17,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But as expected from the Infinity Library,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,it's amazing that I can find whatever I look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:33.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Or rather, we think you are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're so skilled in searching for stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm sorry, but I'd like you to go a bit further.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:39.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}I'm counting on you as well, Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:40.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Lotte, take over for me in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:43.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Okay, Aria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.45,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yuuno sure is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was surprised by it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:53.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The image of that masked man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:04.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This man's abilities are amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:06.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Or rather, I think it's more like impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,These two worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Even with the fastest warps,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:13.11,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,it would take about twenty minutes to cover this much distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:16.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But after blocking a direct hit from Nanoha's new Buster,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:19.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and cleanly initiating a long-range bind,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:23.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,he crept up behind Fate without her noticing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and took her down, in nine minutes' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That means that he's quite adept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Even I couldn't manage that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:32.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What about you, Lotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, no way. Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm not that good at long-range magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:42.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You two clearly divide your duties, with Aria in charge of magic
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:44.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and you in charge of physical stuff, right, Lotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:50.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That got me into so many hardships in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:53.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It made you all the stronger, right?\NYou have to thank us for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:06.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:10.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit uneasy about not being able to use magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but physically, I'm all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:16.07,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,For the time being, Nanoha, until we're called out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.58,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,they want us to live quietly over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:22.01,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I guess it's like we're on standby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:24.68,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They're going to increase the number of armed agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.32,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,and switch the main focus to pursuit research.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.95,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hospitalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:36.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:37.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:40.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I received a call late yesterday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She didn't seem to be that bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:46.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but apparently there are a lot of tests, so it will be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:53.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then how about all of us go together to visit her after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:54.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:57.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She's your friend, right, Suzuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You said you were going to introduce us to her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's better to have a visitation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:03.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that's a little on the merry side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I don't know about the last bit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I think it's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:09.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes... thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, Suzuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.28,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Dear Miss Shamal,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:32.05,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Greetings, this is Suzuka Tsukimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:36.76,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I would like to visit Hayate with my friends after school today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.12,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,but is it all right for us to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Suzuka is such a good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:54.78,Nanoha Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\an5\move(511,626,492,653,35,7500)}{\c&484848&}Please get better soon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:51.00,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,If it is inconvenient for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:54.27,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,please show this photograph to Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:09.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What's this about Testarossa and her group?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:10.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Testarossa and Nanoha, those two mages from the Bureau,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,are going to come visit Hayate today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Because they're friends with Suzuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:22.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, what should we do, what should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:22.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}No, calm down, Shamal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, most of {\i1}Meister{\i0}\NHayate's magical potential
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,is within the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:29.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Unless they give her detailed tests, they can't find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:33.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:36.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,In other words, we just have to be careful that we don't bump into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:40.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It was a mistake to let them see my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:44.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When went to fight them, I should have used transformation magic or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:47.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There's no use regretting things now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:50.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When her friends are visiting, we can step out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:57.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And we'll ask {\i1}Meister{\i0} Hayate and\NDr. Ishida not to mention our names.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:01.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Would Hayate think that was weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We have no other choice.\NI'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:07.60,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\an5\pos(490,479)\c&H8A8B8D&\frz354.7}Hayate Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.05,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hello! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:22.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:24.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, everyone, sit down, sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.87,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:29.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The coat rack is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:31.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:33.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Here, this is a cake from our place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.17,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's really tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Ms. Shamal, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:45.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... I just got a bit worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You can just go inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Or is that a taboo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:52.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:59.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This may be a strange way of putting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but as Hayate's primary doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I really am thankful to all of you, Ms. Shamal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:05.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Ever since you all started living with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:08.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate seems so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:14.75,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Hayate's illness is very difficult to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But we are doing everything we can to combat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:20.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate is the one who is facing the toughest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:24.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But, with all of you and all her friends supporting her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she will get some courage and vitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:29.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So please keep supporting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So that Hayate will be able to fight against her illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I hope Hayate gets well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:51.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,How was your friends' visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all of them were good girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:56.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They said they'd swing by every so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:01.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But you know, it's almost Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:20:59.68,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\an5\c&HAADAB8&\b1\i1\3c&H6BA562&\bord4.0\fs64\frz342.4\move(525.667,718,416.667,453,33,497)}Christmas Days{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.76,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\an5\c&HAADAB8&\b1\i1\3c&H6BA562&\bord4.0\fs64\frz342.4\\pos(417,453)}Christmas Days{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:04.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This will be my first Christmas together with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I hope I can get out of here by then
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:08.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and have a great, fun time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:11.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's right... it would be nice if you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:36.79,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The speed with which the {\i0}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.40,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,is infiltrating into Hayate seems to be steadily increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.73,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,At this rate, she'll only last a month at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:45.70,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,No, perhaps not even that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:55.81,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Something is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:59.98,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,My memory is telling me that this isn't the way it's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:05.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But this is the only thing we can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:12.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'd hate it if Hayate stopped laughing... or even died... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:13.22,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:13.22,Nanoha Device2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(476,650)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:21.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Eisen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:22.83,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:27.91,Nanoha Device2,,0,0,0,,{\i0\b1}Gigant{\i1\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:31.94,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Crush it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.43,0:22:45.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:49.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's not healthy for you to work so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:50.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:51.87,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, Liese...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:53.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,How are things going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:55.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's going bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:57.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono's group is doing their best,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:00.78,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but they are facing the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0}, so it won't be so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:02.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:05.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:08.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,getting you involved in this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:10.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:12.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We are your familiars, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:15.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your wish is our wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:18.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.10,0:23:20.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Durandal is already complete too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:22.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The seal on the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:24.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that it will be fine this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:29.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:40.51,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I won't forget even when I grow up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:48.44,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, the day that we came across each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:53.22,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,In this place, where flowers bloom intensely
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:56.93,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I kept you in tears
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:24:00.33,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I remember the promise
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:06.79,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, the smile that I love so much
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:17.44,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,That day, when the secret door opened
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:24.88,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I was chasing after a small white butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.23,0:24:33.13,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I got lost, and I wanted to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.13,0:24:36.87,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My true wishes, my true feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:41.37,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Maybe you taught those to me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.37,0:24:45.51,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Guarded by such kind feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.51,0:24:49.08,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I was spoiled for all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.08,0:24:52.88,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,How you thought dear of me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.88,0:24:58.85,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, I won't forget all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.38,0:25:11.53,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The {\i0}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i1} is almost complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.53,0:25:13.83,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,but then {\i0}that{\i1} happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.83,0:25:17.60,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Was it coincidence or necessity...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.60,0:25:19.70,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Or even destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:22.94,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The time that had stopped is now running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.94,0:25:26.34,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Next episode of\N{\i0}Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha A's:{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.34,0:25:29.45,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Episode 9: Christmas Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.20,0:25:35.95,Nanoha A's Title2,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(476,480)\blur0.5}Christmas Eve
